        Holding Deposits and Expression-of-Interest Deposits in Queensland: What Sellers Need to Know
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        A holding deposit signals buyer interest but does not create a binding sale in Queensland. Here is how they work, the mistakes sellers make when relying on them, and how to turn buyer interest into a signed contract.
      </p>
    </div>
